<h2>Documentation</h2>

<p>The latest released version of the <b>igraph</b> library is <b>$VERSION</b>.</p>

<ul class="no-bullet download">
<li class="download download-r">
  <span class="name">R package</span>
  <span class="comment">&mdash; for those who use <b>igraph</b> from R.</span>
